# 2. Builds an interpolated discount curve.
# 3. Derives 28-day forwards after each Banxico meeting.
# 4. Converts forwards into market-implied meeting moves.
# 5. Exposes assumptions: basis, interpolation, move size, forward window, DV01.
# 6. Lets users enter policy path scenarios by meeting.
# 7. Computes scenario fair value by tenor.
# 8. Shows trade/risk output for payer/receiver positions.
# 9. Provides Research / Sales / Trading summary panels.
